{"tid":573200,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]《格鬥街區》（BEAT STREET）街機橫向過關","createTime":"2018-02-26T08:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T15:17:25.000Z","uid":72343,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf1aa13b22f8eb9bed835e05990f3281d6a059e8","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/160953_02be966688547d8388cb85bce0d8049f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F160953_02be966688547d8388cb85bce0d8049f.jpg&h=7ff051c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/161319_dacfad0ca86ac0ec30befe55e3430fde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F161319_dacfad0ca86ac0ec30befe55e3430fde.png&h=b509dddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻game畫風同音樂都好正, 好有以前街機feel<br />\n操作雖然好簡單, 單手已經可以出技, 但有得自己連combo, 唔洗chok黎chok去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/161207_928ca6a267e409f2bd74e1fb2ceea4f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F161207_928ca6a267e409f2bd74e1fb2ceea4f2.jpg&h=538fbe94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/161241_dbe8c1faa78c87fb239983a94a896792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F161241_dbe8c1faa78c87fb239983a94a896792.jpg&h=87f53d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n角色好似有7-8隻, 有耐性既完全唔洗課金都解得到<br />\n不過角色level有限, 例如第一隻角Lee唔突只有10lv, 要突上去就要用石<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/161219_f5d47e396dd047ab9b1f722a1bf5dd1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F161219_f5d47e396dd047ab9b1f722a1bf5dd1e.jpg&h=99ce2908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻game仲有得coop 雙打, ios同an platform可以互連, 不過data連線質素一般, 用wifi會穩定D<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/161306_23811873c1f93ba029e73fab017013d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F161306_23811873c1f93ba029e73fab017013d1.jpg&h=a948ef2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然隻game D英文小學生都睇得明, 不過佢都有中文<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(ios:繁中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> an:殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> an D字體仲要好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span><br />\n親切度up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rrGp7R6dYc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrrGp7R6dYc8&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b4d67815\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rrGp7R6dYc8</a><br />\n呢條試玩片係小弟自己錄, 大家當demo睇下啦<br />\n玩single player可以俾你錄低, coop就冇得錄<br />\n仲有得俾你係fb youtube 直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有玩開同有興趣既巴打一齊交流下, 或者留低room id一齊過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/162057_3c5e6bab54402a5dd33f6132786a0061.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F162057_3c5e6bab54402a5dd33f6132786a0061.png&h=5d70ab99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">隻game都有D廣告時不時要你睇, 不過課$15就可以免廣告, 值唔值就見人見智喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/beat-street/id1209083304?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fbeat-street%2Fid1209083304%3Fmt%3D8&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b3d4504e\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/beat-street/id1209083304?mt=8</a><br />\nAN:<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.luckykat.beatstreet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.luckykat.beatstreet&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0c606da8\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.luckykat.beatstreet</a>"},{"pid":"ffca81a794f28884051b8fa4bc727467b126c75a","tid":573200,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"無聊"},{"pid":"3b3dff9b2f5eba00b3fb4e02c6d174881e7bc84c","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21edfa1ad7f72216ce9d98ffc322e1d07e482403","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723ee8f446afe2fb41c2e35fddaf7dcb6ccfbb6e","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09b099957970be487e5e705818e95e51c9a90dd","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d741a9805bfb9134ddb783d0366732e2b71696b","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e52bb69fad6c8484dee4151ab63d8b621532a4","tid":573200,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:19:26.000Z","msg